snippet.title: On The Road - Truck Simulator | Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
On The Road - Truck Simulator will be available for PC on 14th November 2019.

Available on STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/285380/On_The_Road/

Key request: https://www.keymailer.co/g/games/38291
